    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, factory-fresh luster and absolutely no scratches, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that remains supple and an interior that still retains that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber in truly showroom condition.",
