    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical health, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and double VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual shifts with bolt-action precision, and the chassis integrity is verified with a reinforced rear subframe for maximum torsional rigidity. Equipped with the factory Variable M Differential Lock and original suspension geometry, this vehicle offers the precise, analog feedback that defines the M-division's heritage. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is current, presenting a turnkey opportunity for the collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
